Package NationMania.parsing

NationMania.parsing is incharge of updating the DB via Yago Repo.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    YagoCaption
    This class Builds captions for yago entities
    Some from PreferredMeanings files (not yago's)
    and others by manipulating the strings

    Used by YagoSQL for entity captions.
    YagoChecksum
    This Class Calculates the SHA1 checksum of a given file
    It is used by YagoUpdate to validate the SQL script files.
    YagoEntry
    This is a data structure that holds an Yago entry.
    It contains the 4 fields of a given row
    It is the base for YagoEntryFact, YagoEntryNation
    YagoEntryFact
    This is a data structure that holds a parsed fact.
    It contains the 4 fields of a given row
    And data fields as well
    It extends YagoEntry
    YagoEntryFactContainer
    This class Contains all the facts found.
    Updates the facts' types.
    Removes facts under a certain popularity threshold
    and Relations that where waived by user.
    YagoEntryNation
    This is a data structure that holds a parsed nation.
    It contains the 4 fields of a given row
    And data fields as well
    It extends YagoEntry
    YagoParser
    This class parses yago files
    It retrieves entries

    It collects Nations, Facts and Types
    YagoUpdate
    This class takes care of updating the DB based on Yago TSV files
    It tries to do so in a safe manner in order to prevent DB corruption

    Required files are validated & Errors are plotted to the user.

Package NationMania.parsing Description

NationMania.parsing is incharge of updating the DB via Yago Repo.
